data.description: Welcome home! This like new home was just completed in December of 2022 and features a sprawling single story floorplan complete with 4 bedrooms! The home is packed with energy efficient elements throughout. A sleek, modern feel greets you and continues through the entirety of the home. Large modern kitchen with a huge center island and breakfast bar overlooks the living room and provides a clean and modern heart of the home. Situated just minutes from the bustling night life and restaurants of the South Menchaca entertainment district as well as close proximity to the Southpark Meadows shopping district. This home is an amazing value as well as being in the heart of vibrant South Austin. Executed contract will require bank approval.
